								<img src="http://www.bitcointrading.com/forum/Themes/brFinale_2_0/images/useroff.gif" alt="Offline" />
								<a href="http://www.bitcointrading.com/forum/index.php?action=profile;u=1;PHPSESSID=hp70s9d1hbdcpafag006e54sr6" title="View the profile of maplesyrupghost">maplesyrupghost</a>
